<body>
<aside class="language-select"><a href="?lang=en">English</a> / <a href="?lang=ja">Japanese</a></aside>
<header>
  <p
    data-setup="localize"
    data-text-ja="もう忘れてたとは言わせない"
  >Never forget anything again.</p>
  <h1>7kai Tasks</h1>
  <nav><a
    data-setup="show"
    data-show='{"id":"signin"}'
  ><img src="/static/img/button-start.gif"></a></nav>
</header>

<article class="container">
  <ul class="unstyled">
    <li>
      <div>
        <span
          data-setup="localize"
          data-text-ja="タスクを整理し、やるべきことに集中"
        >Rearranging and concentration.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span
          data-setup="localize"
          data-text-ja="チームにも対応、メールやチャットでの依頼をスマートリプレース"
        >Replace an email and IM.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span
          data-setup="localize"
          data-text-ja="ブラウザ拡張も導入すれば、その日の残タスクが一目瞭然"
        >Install Browser Extentions.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</article>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:20px">
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-start-tasks.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="速く"
      >Quick</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="連続登録に対応したタスク登録画面。"
      >Let's register a lot.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="タイトル入力即エンター。"
      >Input and [Enter].</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-coffee.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="軽快で"
      >One hand</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ワンクリックで状態変更。"
      >State change with a single click.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ダブルクリックですぐ編集。"
      >Double-click to edit.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ガントチャートで気軽にリスケ。"
      >Rescheduling by Gantt chart.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-rush.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="時に激しく"
      >Rush</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="その日やる事にスターを付け一気に消化。"
      >Give a star and end it in a day.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:60px">
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-option.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="多彩で"
      >More operation</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="捌き切れないタスクは延期・保留・委任・破棄。"
      >Manage pending and postponement and assign.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="終わらないタスクを溜め込まない。"
      >Postpone or cancel the task that was not over.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-filter.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="豊富で"
      >Grasp</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="４つのソート。"
      >Four sorts.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="５つのフィルター。"
      >Five filters.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="色で分類可能なリスト。"
      >Classify lists with a color.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <div class=""><img src="/static/img/top-killall.png"></div>
      <h2
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="すぐわかる"
      >Extermination</h2>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ブラウザ通知で即キャッチ。"
      >Immediately catch by Browser Notification.</p>
      <p
        data-setup="localize"
        data-text-ja="ヒストリーで後追いも楽々。"
      >Check to follow later by Changes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:60px">
  <a
    style="font-size:3em"
    href="manual"
    data-setup="localize"
    data-text-ja="マニュアルが出来ました"
